 The Kerrighed OS is a Linux-based SSI system which allows you to use
 a cluster as a single SMP machine.
 .
 This package contains the library required to use advanced features
 of the Kerrighed OS.

Package: kerrighed-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Tools for the Kerrighed OS
 The Kerrighed OS is a Linux-based SSI system which allows you to use
 a cluster as a single SMP machine.
 .
 This package contains the tools to manage a Kerrighed cluster.

